ilyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/29\/whatever-you-want-in-paradise\/","url_meta":{"origin":35489,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Jannah: You will have whatever you want in Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 29, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Buraydah ibn al-Hasib reported: A man asked the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, will there be camels in Paradise?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cIf Allah admits you into Paradise, you will have therein whatever your soul desires and pleases your eyes.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2543\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38039,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/07\/29\/ask-allah-firdaus\/","url_meta":{"origin":35489,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Firdaws: One hundred levels in Paradise beneath the Throne","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 29, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019adh ibn Jabal reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever fasts the month of Ramadan, performs the prayers, and makes the Hajj pilgrimage to the House, it is a duty upon Allah to forgive him whether he emigrates in the path of Allah or\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11835,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/25\/al-firdaws-highest-level-paradise\/","url_meta":{"origin":35489,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on al-Firdaws: Ask Allah for the highest level of Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 25, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"'Ubadah ibn al-Samit reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cParadise has one hundred levels, and between every two levels is a distance like that between the heavens and earth. Al-Firdaws\u00a0is its highest level, from which four rivers of Paradise flow, and above is the\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32753,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/12\/jannah-gold-silver-pearls\/","url_meta":{"origin":35489,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Jannah: Gold, silver, and pearl wonders in Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 12, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Musa reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, in Paradise are two gardens with silver vessels and two gardens with golden vessels. Nothing comes between its people looking upon their Lord but a curtain of majesty over His face in the Garden of Eden. In\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37915,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/06\/23\/rivers-in-paradise\/","url_meta":{"origin":35489,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Jannah: Rivers of water, milk, honey, and wine in Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 23, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019awiyah ibn Haydah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, in Paradise there is a sea of water, a sea of honey, a sea of milk, and a sea of wine, and thereafter they branch into rivers.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2571 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19342,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/06\/17\/hereafter-jannah-nar-dua\/","url_meta":{"origin":35489,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Akhirah: Paradise and Hellfire pray for believers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 17, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever asks Allah for Paradise three times, Paradise will say: O Allah, admit him into Paradise! Whoever seeks protection from Hellfire three times, Hellfire will say: O Allah, save him from the Hellfire!\u201d Source: Sunan\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/35489","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/use